<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Worldborne Medical — Physician-Led Clinical Content Review</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --ink:       #0d1117;
    --fog:       #f4f1ec;
    --paper:     #faf8f4;
    --gold:      #b8955a;
    --gold-lt:   #d4b07a;
    --muted:     #6b6560;
    --rule:      rgba(184,149,90,0.25);
    --serif:     'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    --sans:      'DM Sans', sans-serif;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 17px;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── NOISE OVERLAY ── */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 9999;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }

  /* ── TYPOGRAPHY ── */
  h1, h2, h3, h4 { font-family: var(--serif); font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.18; }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 18px 56px;
    background: rgba(250,248,244,0.88);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    transition: padding 0.3s;
  }

  .nav-logo-container {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .nav-logo-img {
    height: 40px;
    width: auto;
  }

  .nav-logo-text {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: var(--ink);
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .nav-logo-text span { color: var(--gold); }

  .nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 38px;
    list-style: none;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .nav-links a {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--gold); }

  .nav-cta {
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper) !important;
    padding: 10px 22px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: background 0.2s !important;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em !important;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--gold) !important; color: var(--ink) !important; }

  /* ── HERO ── */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 120px 56px 80px;
    gap: 60px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -120px; right: -80px;
    width: 580px; height: 580px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(184,149,90,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease 0.1s forwards;
  }
  .hero-eyebrow::before {
    content: '';
    display: inline-block;
    width: 32px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--gold);
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 4.2vw, 4.2rem);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease 0.2s forwards;
  }
  .hero h1 em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .hero-body {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 460px;
    margin-bottom: 44px;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease 0.35s forwards;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 18px;
    align-items: center;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease 0.5s forwards;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--ink);
    padding: 15px 34px;
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--gold-lt); transform: translateY(-1px); }

  /* ── HERO VISUAL (PORTFOLIO BOX) ── */
  .hero-visual {
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeIn 1s ease 0.4s forwards;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .portfolio-box {
    background: var(--ink);
    border-radius: 4px;
    padding: 32px 36px;
    color: var(--paper);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    max-width: 380px;
    width: 100%;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }
  .portfolio-box::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--gold), var(--gold-lt), transparent);
  }

  .profile-container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .profile-img {
    width: 110px;
    height: 110px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid var(--gold);
    object-fit: cover;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .profile-name {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    color: var(--paper);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .profile-title {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .card-stat-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--paper);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .stat-num span { color: var(--gold); font-size: 1.8rem; }
  .stat-label { font-size: 0.7rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; }

  .card-divider { height: 1px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); margin-bottom: 24px; }

  .card-badge {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    background: rgba(184,149,90,0.12);
    border: 1px solid rgba(184,149,90,0.3);
    padding: 10px 18px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--gold-lt);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }
  .badge-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--gold); animation: pulse 2s infinite; }

  /* ── SECTION BASE ── */
  section { padding: 110px 56px; }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .section-label::before { content: ''; display: inline-block; width: 28px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); }

  .section-h {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.2vw, 3.2rem);
    max-width: 640px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .section-sub {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  /* ── PROBLEM BAND ── */
  .problem-band {
    background: var(--fog);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding: 80px 56px;
  }
  .problem-band p {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.2vw, 2.1rem);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.55;
    max-width: 860px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .problem-band p em { color: var(--gold); font-style: italic; }

  /* ── SERVICES ── */
  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2px;
    background: var(--rule);
  }

  .service-card {
    background: var(--paper);
    padding: 44px 36px;
    position: relative;
    transition: background 0.25s;
    cursor: default;
  }
  .service-card:hover { background: var(--fog); }
  .service-card:hover .sc-arrow { transform: translate(4px, -4px); }

  .sc-num {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: rgba(13,17,23,0.06);
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    transition: color 0.25s;
  }
  .service-card:hover .sc-num { color: rgba(184,149,90,0.15); }

  .sc-title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 1.45rem;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .sc-body { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 28px; }

  .sc-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .sc-tag {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 40px;
  }

  .sc-arrow {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--gold);
    display: inline-block;
    transition: transform 0.2s;
  }

  /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(22px); }
    to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from { opacity: 0; }
    to   { opacity: 1; }
  }
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50%      { opacity: 0.4; transform: scale(0.8); }
  }

  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(28px);
    transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    nav { padding: 18px 24px; }
    .nav-links { display: none; }
    .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 100px 24px 60px; }
    section, .problem-band { padding: 72px 24px; }
    .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .portfolio-box { margin: 0 auto; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<nav>
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo-container">
    <img src="logo.png" alt="Worldborne Logo" class="nav-logo-img">
    <div class="nav-logo-text">Worldborne<span>.</span></div>
  </a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
    <li><a href="#who">Who We Serve</a></li>
    <li><a href="#process">Process</a></li>
    <li><a href="#contact" class="nav-cta">Book a Call</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-left">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Physician-Led Clinical Review</div>
    <h1>Medical content<br>held to a<br><em>clinical standard.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-body">
      Worldborne Medical embeds physician oversight into your content pipeline — protecting your audience, your authority, and your search rankings.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#contact" class="btn-primary">Schedule a Review Call</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-visual">
    <div class="portfolio-box">
      <div class="profile-container">
        <img src="profile.png" alt="Thomas Hatzilabrou" class="profile-img">
        <h3 class="profile-name">Clinical Oversight</h3>
        <p class="profile-title">Physician-Led Review</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-stat-grid">
        <div class="stat-block">
          <div class="stat-num">100<span>%</span></div>
          <div class="stat-label">MD-Reviewed</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-block">
          <div class="stat-num">E-E-A-T</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Verified</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-divider"></div>
      <div class="card-badge">
        <span class="badge-dot"></span>
        Now accepting new clients
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="problem-band">
  <p>
    Google's helpful content updates have made one thing clear: health and legal publishers that lack genuine clinical oversight are <em>losing ground to those that don't.</em> The stakes aren't just rankings — they're reader safety.
  </p>
</div>

<section id="services">
  <div class="section-label">What We Do</div>
  <h2 class="section-h">A full suite of physician-led content services</h2>
  <p class="section-sub">From individual article audits to embedded editorial oversight, our services are built around one principle: clinical accuracy is non-negotiable.</p>

  <div class="services-grid reveal">
    <div class="service-card">
      <div class="sc-num">01</div>
      <div class="sc-title">Clinical Content Review</div>
      <p class="sc-body">Physician review of health articles, condition pages, treatment guides, and symptom explainers. Every claim verified against current medical literature.</p>
      <div class="sc-tags">
        <span class="sc-tag">Fact-Check</span>
        <span class="sc-tag">Citations</span>
        <span class="sc-tag">Corrections</span>
      </div>
      <span class="sc-arrow">↗</span>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <div class="sc-num">02</div>
      <div class="sc-title">Medical SEO Strategy</div>
      <p class="sc-body">Keyword research, topical authority mapping, and YMYL content architecture designed by physicians who understand both clinical nuance and search intent.</p>
      <div class="sc-tags">
        <span class="sc-tag">YMYL</span>
        <span class="sc-tag">E-E-A-T</span>
        <span class="sc-tag">Topical Maps</span>
      </div>
      <span class="sc-arrow">↗</span>
    </div>
    <div class="service-card">
      <div class="sc-num">03</div>
      <div class="sc-title">Legal-Medical Content</div>
      <p class="sc-body">Expert medical review for personal injury, medical malpractice, and health-law content to ensure clinical claims are defensible and medically sound.</p>
      <div class="sc-tags">
        <span class="sc-tag">Compliance</span>
        <span class="sc-tag">Liability</span>
        <span class="sc-tag">Accuracy</span>
      </div>
      <span class="sc-arrow">↗</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</body>
</html>
